    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Merchants selling second-hand books, leaflets, and prints of little value, such as those working outdoors alongside the Seine River in Paris. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
